                f"MASSIVE OBV ACCUMULATION SHAKEOUT: OBV={obv_value:,.0f} (POSITIVE_EXTREME), "
                f"vol={volume_ratio:.2f}x, price down {change_5m:.1f}%, down_energy=0, "
